          <p>{{ "Understanding the demographics of your customers enables you to identify hot spot areas and locations which other sites (competitor) are supplying. We create profiles that enable you to understand the propensity for different types of customer to shop with your brand." | i18n }}</p>
        </figcaption>

        <div class="image-background" style='background-image: url("{% cloudinary '/location planning/customerprofiling.jpg', 'w_550,f_auto' %}")'>
          
        </div>
      </figure>

      <figure class="gallery-block">
        <figcaption class="gallery-block__content">
          <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "Key Driver Analysis" | i18n }}</h2>
          <p>{{ "Key drivers of store performance help you understand over and under performance across your estate in addition to which new locations will be successful. Competition, retail environment, urbanity, customer type, location type (city centre, retail park, local parade, rural) and micro site locations all combine with operational measures." | i18n }}</p>
          <p>{{ "It is our job to unpick them to provide a transparent fact base for you to work from." | i18n }}</p>
        </figcaption>

        <img src="{% cloudinary '/location planning/keydriveranalysis.png', 'w_550,f_auto' %}" srcset="{% cloudinary '/location planning/keydriveranalysis.png', 'w_550,f_auto,dpr_2.0' %} 2x" class="gallery-block__media" alt="Key Driver Analysis">
      </figure>

      <figure class="gallery-block">
        <figcaption class="gallery-block__content">
          <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "Sales Cannibalisation" | i18n }}</h2>
          <p>{{ "Will opening a new site impact the sales of shops nearby? When it does it is an example of sales cannibalisation. If possible we evaluate real world examples of store openings before we build a model to forecast sales performance impacts. Understanding whether you should open in a location to stop a competitor impact is an important investment decision. Not all impacts are the same. A new drive thru or shopping centre location may not hit a high street location nearby if the customer mission to visit is different. Mobility data modelling insights help us to answer these dilemmas." | i18n }}</p>
        </figcaption>

        <img src="{% cloudinary '/location planning/salescannibalisation.png', 'w_550,f_auto' %}" srcset="{% cloudinary '/location planning/salescannibalisation.png', 'w_550,f_auto,dpr_2.0' %} 2x" class="gallery-block__media" alt="Sales Cannibalisation">
      </figure>

      <figure class="gallery-block">
        <figcaption class="gallery-block__content">
          <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "Catchment Creation" | i18n }}</h2>
          <p>{{ "Not all stores pull from the same catchments. We can use your customer postcode level data, mobility data or our towns and suburbs data to build the effective market from where potential consumers will travel from." | i18n }}</p>
        </figcaption>

        <img src="{% cloudinary '/location planning/catchmentcreation.png', 'w_550,f_auto' %}" srcset="{% cloudinary '/location planning/catchmentcreation.png', 'w_550,f_auto,dpr_2.0' %} 2x" class="gallery-block__media" alt="Catchment Creation">
      </figure>

      <figure class="gallery-block">
        <figcaption class="gallery-block__content">
          <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "Store Sales Forecasting" | i18n }}</h2>
          <p>{{ "Opening a store is one of the single biggest investments you'll make, and this is why many of our customers want to be confident that they make the decision based on factual evidence." | i18n }}</p>
          <p>{{ "Our data scientists will carry out extensive analysis combining your information with our suite of data. We create bespoke sales forecasting models which are relevant for the use case, whether that be a gravity model, spatial regression, analogue model or a combination." | i18n }}</p>
        </figcaption>

        <img src="{% cloudinary '/location planning/storesalesforecasting.png', 'w_550,f_auto' %}" srcset="{% cloudinary '/location planning/storesalesforecasting.png', 'w_550,f_auto,dpr_2.0' %} 2x" class="gallery-block__media" alt="Store Sales Forecasting">
      </figure>

      <figure class="gallery-block">
        <figcaption class="gallery-block__content">
          <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "Network Blueprints" | i18n }}</h2>
          <p>{{ "Understanding how many stores your business can reach is a key part in your strategic growth plan. In addition, a clear ranked output of the highest potential locations will enable your surveyors to prioritise the best available sites." | i18n }}</p>
          <p>{{ "The benefits of a network strategy, especially those that include different scenarios for different strategic routes are valuable in the short and long term." | i18n }}</p>
        </figcaption>

        <img src="{% cloudinary '/location planning/networkblueprints.png', 'w_550,f_auto' %}" srcset="{% cloudinary '/location planning/networkblueprints.png', 'w_550,f_auto,dpr_2.0' %} 2x" class="gallery-block__media" alt="Network Blueprints">
      </figure>

      <figure class="gallery-block">
        <figcaption class="gallery-block__content">
          <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "International Expansion" | i18n }}</h2>
          <p>{{ "What new country should we enter next? Your future business growth is dependent on making the best decisions about network expansion." | i18n }}</p>
          <p>{{ "We have helped 100s of companies understand the demand potential across different countries, how consumers differ and key insights around the potential number of sites that could open. The benefits of international research can be huge. Our global database and wide network of offices has helped us to carry out projects in over 60 countries." | i18n }}</p>
        </figcaption>

        <img src="{% cloudinary '/location planning/internationexpansion.png', 'w_550,f_auto' %}" srcset="{% cloudinary '/location planning/internationexpansion.png', 'w_550,f_auto,dpr_2.0' %} 2x" class="gallery-block__media" alt="International Expansion">
